  "body": "While using the `--datadir` option with geth (latest windows build) , It requires entry of file path as `geth.exe --datadir=\"C:/blockchain/\"` while it should have file path in windows style. The `geth help` gave and example like `C:\\xxx\\xxx` which is a contradiction. btw when providing file path as `--datadir=\"C:\\blockchain\\\"` gave an error. Seems like it requires unix styled path entry.\n\n(Note: notice the forward and the backwards slash )\n",
