    "body": "This is probably caused by the console.\n\n`geth>geth.exe --datadir \"H:\\blockchain\\\"` translates to a datadir in of `H:/blockchain\"` which is invalid. You have 2 options:\n1. `geth>geth.exe --datadir \"H:\\blockchain\"`\n2. `geth>geth.exe --datadir \"H:\\blockchain\\\\\"`\n\nBoth have the same semantics.\n",
